SUMMARY:Rest Retreat for Mamas
DESCRIPTION:Barefoot Yoga Studio and Davis Women’s Circles are joining together to bring you an uplifting rest retreat you wouldn’t want to miss. Mama\, do you long to create more literal and figurative spaces for rest in your life? Have you noticed that mothering in a “grind” culture compels us to hustle\, achieve and push ourselves constantly? If you’d like to slow down\, flourish more\, and grow your village\, this retreat is for you! \nCome explore and experience various types of rest\, including a sound bath\, gentle yoga\, stretching\, and a special women’s circle on rest. \nThis intimate event will be located in Barefoot Yoga Studio’s beautiful new Woodland location\, and will include nutritious and tasty refreshments.\nEarly-bird special: $50 through 2/14; regular price: $60; at the door: $70.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/rest-retreat-for-mamas/
LOCATION:Barefoot Yoga Studio Woodland\, 601 Main St #210\, Woodland\, CA\, 95695
