SUMMARY:Intuitive Soul Stories: Oracle Card Making Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Iama Embodied Community\nUnlock the stories and symbols that l
 ive within you in this gentle\, intuitive collage workshop with guest faci
 litator Rachel Hodge.\nThis isn’t about being an “artist”—it’s a
 bout curiosity\, intuition\, and self-discovery. Using simple images and c
 ollage\, you’ll create a personal deck of oracle-style cards that reflec
 t different parts of your inner world. Each card becomes a “soul compani
 on\,” offering clarity\, grounding\, and a direct line to your own innat
 e wisdom.\nNo artistic experience is needed—just bring your curiosity an
 d openness. Materials will be provided\, and the space is relaxed\, reflec
 tive\, and supportive.\n\n📅 **Date & Time**: Monday Mar 16\, 5-8 PM\n
 📍 **Location**: 727 T St. Sacramento\, Ca\, 95811\n💜 **Cost $25\, Ve
 nmo @Rachel-Hodge-30\, or Cash.**\n✨ **No artistic experience/ skills ne
 cessary.**\n📩 **RSVP/ Questions? Reach out at** embody.iama@gmail.com o
 r suniaitherapy@outlook.com\n🔗 **Follow us on Instagram:** [@embody.iam
 a](https://www.instagram.com/embody.iama)\n\nPS: we meet in the social hal
 l of Parkview Presbyterian Church. Please find us through the back entranc
 e\, the brown gate on Solons alley. You may park in the back\, move the or
 ange post to park and please return it when you leave.
